  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>This hotel is offered on a bed and breakfast basis, perfect if you want a comfortable place to stay and want to sample some of the famous French cuisine Chamonix has to offer.</p>
<p>Each morning a continental buffet breakfast is served, with additional hot options</p>
<p>For evening meals there's an on site gastronomic restaurant or a choice of local restaurants within five minutes' walking distance.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
