  <description><![CDATA[<p>The Hotel Morgane has a fantastic central location in <a data-udi="umb://document/6d1f6b40d62d48a6acbcf99f87501ea0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6d1f6b40d62d48a6acbcf99f87501ea0}" title="Chamonix">Chamonix</a>, offering high quality accommodation with fantastic mountain views. The hotel also has a wellness area with a swimming pool which is ideal after a day on the slopes.</p>
<h2>Central location</h2>
<p>Situated in the centre of <a data-udi="umb://document/6d1f6b40d62d48a6acbcf99f87501ea0" href="/{localLink:umb://document/6d1f6b40d62d48a6acbcf99f87501ea0}" title="Chamonix">Chamonix</a> at the foot of Mont Blanc, the boutique Hotel Morgane has a charming interior and a relaxing atmosphere surrounded with mountain views.</p>
<p>Situated only 90 metres from the Aiguille du Midi cable car, you have fantastic access to the Vallée Blanche, or alternatively there is a ski shuttle service to the slopes offered by the hotel for easy access to the ski areas around Chamonix.</p>
<h2>Modern and comfortable</h2>
<p>All of the rooms in the Hotel Le Morgane have a unique and contemporary design, furnished to a high standard. Many of the rooms have wonderful views over the Mont-Blanc or B<span>révent, so it's ideal for relaxing after a day on the slopes. </span></p>
<h2><span>Soothing spa</span></h2>
<p>After a day of exploring you can relax and unwind in the spa and wellness area which features an indoor heated swimming pool and a steam room and sauna, to soak your achy ski legs. <span>To fully recharge, treatments and massages are available locally. </span></p>]]></description>
