  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Rooms </strong>sleep two people and are around 20m². The rooms feature a double bed and a balcony with mountain view. These rooms are also available for sole occupancy, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms </strong>sleep two people and are around 22m². These rooms feature twin beds and have a balcony with mountain views, usually over the Mont Blanc massif.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suite </strong>sleep two to three people and are around 30m².  These rooms have a double or twin beds, and an additional single sofa bed and a balcony with mountain views. These rooms are available on request, please call us to book this room type.</p>
<p><strong>Room facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Balcony or terrace</li>
<li>Bath with shower head attachment or shower room</li>
<li>WC</li>
<li>TV with English speaking channels</li>
<li>Tea and coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Bath robes</li>
<li>Hair dryer</li>
<li>Slippers</li>
<li>Towels and bed linen</li>
<li>Desk</li>
<li>Ironing facilities</li>
<li>Mini bar</li>
<li>Daily house keeping is included</li>
<li>Baby cots are available on request (Free) for children under 2 years</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
